[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    130[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    131[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The code reads top-to-bottom in a pedagogically sound order:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    132[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. Configuration and constants (context-setting, including measure weights)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    133[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 2. Ontology loading (the knowledge base)
